OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled in honour of man
OL,4,Cthat brought the stars to Batley
OL,6,FHundreds gathered outside the former
OL,7,FBatley Variety Club to celebrate the
OL,8,Fman who brought "a little Las Vegas"
OL,9,Fto Yorkshire.
OL,11,FBefore opening the club in 1967,
OL,12,FCorrigan and his wife Betty went to
OL,13,FLas Vegas to develop their design for
OL,14,Fa new venue.
OL,16,FThe club was known as the "Vegas of
OL,17,Fthe North" and attracted the best acts
OL,18,Fin show business, both from the UK and
OL,19,FUSA.
