OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled in honour of man
OL,4,Cthat brought the stars to Batley
OL,6,FThe accolades continued at event held
OL,7,Fto unveil the plaque, with messages
OL,8,Ffrom Neil Sedaka, Cliff Richard and
OL,9,Fone from Shirley Bassey.
OL,11,FBassey said: "James, always the joker
OL,12,Fasked me if I'd like to go for dinner
OL,13,Fone evening. I accepted and we
OL,14,Farranged for the Friday after the show.
OL,16,F"I got all dressed up in a mink jacket
OL,17,Fand a cocktail gown. You took me to a
OL,18,Ffish and chip takeaway. When the
OL,19,Fopposition approached me to play other
OL,20,Fvenues, I refused."
