OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled in honour of man
OL,4,Cthat brought the stars to Batley
OL,6,FBatley Variety Club closed in 1978
OL,7,Fbefore reopening as the Frontier a few
OL,8,Fyears later. It then closed again in
OL,9,F2016 and reopened as a gym.
OL,11,FAmong the stars who turned out in
OL,12,Fperson for the plaque unveiling was
OL,13,FBritish comedian and entertainer,
OL,14,FBernie Clifton, who said he was
OL,15,F"thrilled" to be back at the venue.
OL,17,F"I'm thrilled and delighted to be back
OL,18,Fat Batley Variety Club, where it
OL,19,Fchanged my life.
