OL,4,Cthat brought the stars to Batley
OL,6,F"My life was changed here 53 years
OL,7,Fago. I went on, I did my opening gag."
OL,9,FThe blue plaque is now on display to
OL,10,Fthe public and will remain on the side
OL,11,Fof the building as a lasting reminder
OL,12,Fof James Corrigan's legacy.
